   Poomekum, Potchakorn; Sorsoontornnirat, Thanapat; Suriyawong, Arisara; Topiya, Pimmada; Fugkeaw, Somchart, Thammasat Univ, Sirindhorn Int Inst Technol, Sch Informat Comp \& Commun Technol ICT, Pathum Thani 12000, Thailand.},
DOI = {10.1109/ACCESS.2026.3659626},
